eligibility.inclusivecriteria:
Recipient subjects: 
1) severely obese (BMI: > 35 kg/m2); 
2) post-pubertal adolescents (14-18 years). 
3) 40 males and 40 females

Gut microbiome donors: 
1) healthy; 
2) 18-28 years; 
3) BMI: 18.5-24.9 kg/m2; 
4) exercise at least 3.5 hours per week; 
5) well-balanced healthy diet; 
6) regular bowel habit; 
7) normal insulin sensitivity (by OGTT/Matsuda index)
8) normal fasting lipids
9) normal blood pressure.
